1.Name: The Unreached Dream
1.Desc: After using Skill <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> time(s) in a single turn, the next Skill use in the current turn will not consume Skill Points.

2.Name: The Unfulfilled Happiness
2.Desc: Increases DMG dealt by Ultimate by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak>.

3.Name: The Untamed Will
3.Desc: Skill Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nBasic ATK Lv. +1, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>10</unbreak>.

4.Name: The Unsung Life
4.Desc: If the target of the Ultimate does not possess Quantum Weakness, Quantum Weakness will be applied during the Ultimate and reduces the target's Quantum RES by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> for <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> turn(s).

5.Name: The Nameless Watch
5.Desc: Ultimate Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.\nTalent Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. <unbreak>15</unbreak>.

6.Name: The Endless Pilgrimage
6.Desc: When the turn begins, immediately recovers 1 Skill Point for allies. Increases the maximum stacks for the DMG boost provided by his own Skill by <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> stacks. DMG dealt by his Skill ignores <unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak> of DEF.

101501.Name: Kanshou and Bakuya
101501.Desc: Deals Quantum DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of <unbreak>Archer's</unbreak> ATK to one designated enemy.

101502.Name: Caladbolg: Fake Spiral Sword
101502.Desc: Enters the "Circuit Connection" state. Deals Quantum DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of <unbreak>Archer's</unbreak> ATK to one designated enemy target. In the "Circuit Connection" state, the turn does not end after using Skill, and increases the DMG dealt by <unbreak>Archer's</unbreak> Skill by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color>. This effect can be stacked up to <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> times, lasting until he exits the "Circuit Connection" state. After actively using Skill <unbreak>#5[i]</unbreak> times or when there are insufficient Skill Points, using Skill again causes him to exit the "Circuit Connection" state and ends the turn. Exits the "Circuit Connection" state after all enemies have been defeated in each wave.

101503.Name: Unlimited Blade Works
101503.Desc: Deals Quantum DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of <unbreak>Archer's</unbreak> ATK to one designated enemy and gains <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> Charge, up to a maximum of <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> Charge.

101504.Name: Mind's Eye (True)
101504.Desc: When <unbreak>Archer's</unbreak> teammate attacks an enemy target, <unbreak>Archer</unbreak> consumes 1 Charge and immediately launches <u>Follow-up ATK</u> on the primary target, dealing Quantum DMG equal to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> of <unbreak>Archer's</unbreak> ATK and recovering 1 Skill Point.

101506.Name: Attack
101506.Desc: Attacks an enemy, and when the battle starts, reduces their Toughness of the corresponding Type.

101507.Name: Clairvoyance
101507.Desc: Immediately attacks the enemy. After entering combat, deals Quantum DMG equal to <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> of <unbreak>Archer's</unbreak> ATK to all enemies and gains <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> Charge.

101509.Name: End
101509.Desc: Exits the "Circuit Connection" state and ends the turn.

1.PointDesc: When <unbreak>Archer</unbreak> is on the field, increases the maximum Skill Point limit by <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak>.

After allies gain a Skill Point, if there are <unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak> Skill Points or more, increases <unbreak>Archer's</unbreak> CRIT DMG by <unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak> for <unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak> turns.
